Package: xtfifevd
Type: Package
Title: Fixed Effects Filtered and Vector Decomposition for Panel Data
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Muhammad", "Alkhalaf", email = "muhammedalkhalaf@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-2677-9246"))
Description: Implements the Fixed Effects Vector Decomposition (FEVD) estimator
    of Plumper and Troeger (2007) <doi:10.1093/pan/mpm002> and the Fixed Effects
    Filtered (FEF) and FEF-IV estimators of Pesaran and Zhou (2016)
    <doi:10.1080/07474938.2015.1032164>. Provides consistent standard errors
    for time-invariant regressors in panel data models using the corrected
    variance estimator of Pesaran and Zhou (2016, Econometric Reviews). Supports
    FEVD (three-stage), FEF (two-stage), and FEF-IV (instrumental variables)
    methods with optional comparison of corrected versus raw standard errors.
